{"title":"redis安装","date":"2018-07-13T19:51:00.000Z","link":"post/153","categories":["Redis"],"updated":"2019-06-23T14:31:53.841Z","content":"<p>####进入系统软件目录<br><figure class=\"highlight plain\"><div><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">cd /usr/local/</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure></p>\n<h4 id=\"解压\">解压<a href=\"post/153#解压\"></a></h4><figure class=\"highlight plain\"><div><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">tar -zxvf redis-3.0.0-rc2.tar.gz -C /usr/local/</span><br><span class=\"line\">cd ./redis-3.0.0-rc2</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure>\n<h4 id=\"编译\">编译<a href=\"post/153#编译\"></a></h4><p><strong>进行编译 ，前提是需要有gcc库</strong><br><figure class=\"highlight plain\"><div><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">make   </span><br><span class=\"line\">//出现Hint: It&apos;s a good idea to run &apos;make test&apos; ;)</span><br><span class=\"line\">说明编译成功</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure></p>\n<h4 id=\"安装redis\">安装redis<a href=\"post/153#安装redis\"></a></h4><figure class=\"highlight plain\"><div><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"> cd ./src/</span><br><span class=\"line\">make install</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure>\n<p>安装完成<br><img src=\"https://github.com/1056438464/1056438464.github.io/raw/master/images/3304785728.png\" alt><br><a id=\"more\"></a></p>\n<h4 id=\"创建redis的配置文件夹和脚本文件夹\">创建redis的配置文件夹和脚本文件夹<a href=\"post/153#创建redis的配置文件夹和脚本文件夹\"></a></h4><figure class=\"highlight plain\"><div><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">mkdir -p /usr/local/redis/etc</span><br><span class=\"line\">mkdir -p /usr/local/redis/bin</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure>\n<h4 id=\"移动配置文件\">移动配置文件<a href=\"post/153#移动配置文件\"></a></h4><figure class=\"highlight plain\"><div><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">cd /usr/local/redis-3.0.0-rc2/</span><br><span class=\"line\">cp redis.conf  /usr/local/redis/etc/</span><br><span class=\"line\">cd ./src/</span><br><span class=\"line\">mv mkreleasehdr.sh  redis-benchmark redis-check-aof redis-check-dump redis-cli redis-server  /usr/local/redis/bin/</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure>\n<h4 id=\"修改配置文件，实现后台启动\">修改配置文件，实现后台启动<a href=\"post/153#修改配置文件，实现后台启动\"></a></h4><p><strong>需要打开配置文件设置daemonized  改成yes</strong><br><figure class=\"highlight plain\"><div><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">vim  ./redis/etc/redis.conf</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://github.com/1056438464/1056438464.github.io/raw/master/images/4241125356.png\" alt><br><strong>还需修改数据文件存放修改设置</strong><br><img src=\"https://github.com/1056438464/1056438464.github.io/raw/master/images/1986964787.png\" alt></p>\n<h4 id=\"启动redis\">启动redis<a href=\"post/153#启动redis\"></a></h4><p>启动时并指定配置文件**<br><img src=\"https://github.com/1056438464/1056438464.github.io/raw/master/images/4122044545.png\" alt><br><figure class=\"highlight plain\"><div><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">/usr/local/redis/bin/redis-server /usr/local/redis/etc/redis.conf</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://github.com/1056438464/1056438464.github.io/raw/master/images/2029339704.png\" alt class=\"article-img\"></p>\n<h4 id=\"启动成功-查看进程\">启动成功 查看进程<a href=\"post/153#启动成功-查看进程\"></a></h4><p><img src=\"https://github.com/1056438464/1056438464.github.io/raw/master/images/1132722273.png\" alt class=\"article-img\"></p>\n<h4 id=\"进入redis中\">进入redis中<a href=\"post/153#进入redis中\"></a></h4><figure class=\"highlight plain\"><div><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">/usr/local/redis/bin/redis-cli</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure>\n<p><img src=\"https://github.com/1056438464/1056438464.github.io/raw/master/images/1811239977.png\" alt><br>关闭redis客户单进程<br>quit 或者ctrl+c<br>关闭redis服务端进程<br>/usr/local/redis/bin/redis-cli shutdown</p>\n","prev":{"title":"git 添加文件未识别","link":"post/157"},"next":{"title":"Orcale存储过程事物","link":"post/145"},"plink":"https://1056438464.github.io/post/153/"}